                    "description": "As freelance multimedia journalist in East Africa (first in Kenya and currently based in Kigali, Rwanda), I am focussing on a divers spectrum of (international) topics and I produce articles, photo series, audio reports, videos and multimedia stories. \n\nI work and / or have worked for: Al Jazeera English, Deutsche Welle, Sydney Morning Herald, VPRO Bureau Buitenland, Algemeen Dagblad, De Groene Amsterdammer, Nieuwe Revu, Knack Magazine, Oneworld Magazine, Opzij, Runners World, Vakblad voor de Bloemisterij, Reformatorisch Dagblad and many more.\n\nI love to travel and I am available for assignments in East Africa and beyond. Email me at eva@storiesbyeva.com. \n\nOnline: \nwww.storiesbyeva.com \nFacebook: www.facebook.com/storiesbyeva/\nTwitter: www.twitter.com/EvaDeVries84\nInstagram: www.instagram.com/EvaDeVries84",
